#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.to_csv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.to\\_csv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:1 of
msgid "Write object to a comma-separated values (csv) file."
msgstr "将对象写入逗号分隔值（csv）文件。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:3 of
msgid ""
"File path. If path is a string with wildcard e.g. '/to/path/out-*.csv', "
"to_csv will try to write multiple files, for instance, chunk (0, 0) will "
"write data into '/to/path/out-0.csv'. If path is a string without "
"wildcard, all data will be written into a single file."
msgstr ""
"文件路径。如果路径是包含通配符的字符串，例如 '/to/path/out-*.csv'，to_csv"
" 将尝试写入多个文件，例如，块 (0, 0) 将数据写入 '/to/path/out-0.csv'。"
"如果路径是不包含通配符的字符串，所有数据将写入单个文件。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:10 of
msgid "String of length 1. Field delimiter for the output file."
msgstr "长度为 1 的字符串。输出文件的字段分隔符。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:12 of
msgid "Missing data representation."
msgstr "缺失数据表示。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:14 of
msgid "Format string for floating point numbers."
msgstr "浮点数的格式字符串。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:16 of
msgid "Columns to write."
msgstr "要写入的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:18 of
msgid ""
"Write out the column names. If a list of strings is given it is assumed "
"to be aliases for the column names."
msgstr "写出列名。如果给定字符串列表，则假定它们是列名的别名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:21 of
msgid "Write row names (index)."
msgstr "写入行名称（索引）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:23 of
msgid ""
"Column label for index column(s) if desired. If None is given, and "
"`header` and `index` are True, then the index names are used. A sequence "
"should be given if the object uses MultiIndex. If False do not print "
"fields for index names. Use index_label=False for easier importing in R."
msgstr ""
"如果需要，为索引列指定列标签。如果为 None，并且 `header` 和 `index` 为 "
"True，则使用索引名称。如果对象使用 MultiIndex，则应提供序列。如果为 False"
"，则不打印索引名称的字段。使用 index_label=False 便于在 R 中导入。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:29 of
msgid "Python write mode, default 'w'."
msgstr "Python 写入模式，默认为 'w'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:31 of
msgid ""
"A string representing the encoding to use in the output file, defaults to"
" 'utf-8'."
msgstr "表示在输出文件中使用的编码的字符串，默认为 'utf-8'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:34 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If str, represents compression mode. If dict, value at 'method' is the "
"compression mode. Compression mode may be any of the following possible "
"values: {'infer', 'gzip', 'bz2', 'zip', 'xz', None}. If compression mode "
"is 'infer' and `path_or_buf` is path-like, then detect compression mode "
"from the following extensions: '.gz', '.bz2', '.zip' or '.xz'. (otherwise"
" no compression). If dict given and mode is 'zip' or inferred as 'zip', "
"other entries passed as additional compression options."
msgstr ""
"如果为 str，表示压缩模式。如果为 dict，则 'method' 的值为压缩模式。压缩"
"模式可以是以下任意值：{'infer', 'gzip', 'bz2', 'zip', 'xz', None}。如果"
"压缩模式为 'infer' 且 `path_or_buf` 为路径形式，则从以下扩展名检测压缩"
"模式：'.gz', '.bz2', '.zip' 或 '.xz'（否则不压缩）。如果给定 dict 且模式"
"为 'zip' 或推断为 'zip'，其他条目将作为额外压缩选项传递。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:43 of
msgid ""
"Defaults to csv.QUOTE_MINIMAL. If you have set a `float_format` then "
"floats are converted to strings and thus csv.QUOTE_NONNUMERIC will treat "
"them as non-numeric."
msgstr ""
"默认为 csv.QUOTE_MINIMAL。如果设置了 `float_format`，则浮点数将被转换为"
"字符串，因此 csv.QUOTE_NONNUMERIC 将其视为非数值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:47 of
msgid "String of length 1. Character used to quote fields."
msgstr "长度为 1 的字符串。用于引用字段的字符。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:49 of
msgid ""
"The newline character or character sequence to use in the output file. "
"Defaults to `os.linesep`, which depends on the OS in which this method is"
" called ('\\n' for linux, '\\r\\n' for Windows, i.e.)."
msgstr ""
"输出文件中使用的换行符或换行符序列。默认为 `os.linesep`，它取决于调用此"
"方法的操作系统（Linux 为 '\\n'，Windows 为 '\\r\\n'，等等）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:53 of
msgid "Rows to write at a time."
msgstr "一次写入的行数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:55 of
msgid "Format string for datetime objects."
msgstr "日期时间对象的格式字符串。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:57 of
msgid "Control quoting of `quotechar` inside a field."
msgstr "控制字段内 `quotechar` 的引用方式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:59 of
msgid ""
"String of length 1. Character used to escape `sep` and `quotechar` when "
"appropriate."
msgstr "长度为 1 的字符串。用于在适当时转义 `sep` 和 `quotechar` 的字符。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:62 of
msgid "Character recognized as decimal separator. E.g. use ',' for European data."
msgstr "识别为小数分隔符的字符。例如，欧洲数据使用 ','。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:66 of
msgid ""
"If path_or_buf is None, returns the resulting csv format as a string. "
"Otherwise returns None."
msgstr "如果 path_or_buf 为 None，则返回结果 csv 格式的字符串。否则返回 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:72 of
msgid ":py:obj:`read_csv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_csv.to_csv:73 of
msgid "Load a CSV file into a DataFrame."
msgstr "将 CSV 文件加载到 DataFrame 中。"

